## ðŸš€ Installation

**Using pip:**
```bash
pip install agent-farm
```

**Using uv (recommended):**
```bash
uv add agent-farm
```

**From source:**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/bjoernbethge/agent-farm.git
cd agent-farm
uv sync --dev
```

---

## ðŸŽ¯ Quick Start

**Run the MCP server:**
```bash
agent-farm
```

**Or as a module:**
```bash
python -m agent_farm
```

